# === User uploads ===
# The current files in admin/assets/uploads/ are demo content (product
# images, cover, logo) and are intentionally kept in the repository.
# If you later want to stop tracking NEW user uploads, uncomment the
# lines below and keep the demo files via "!":
#
# admin/assets/uploads/*
# !admin/assets/uploads/4.jpg
# !admin/assets/uploads/5.jpg
# !admin/assets/uploads/6.jpg
# !admin/assets/uploads/7.jpg
